<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Awk on Min Soe Han</title><link>https://minsoehan.com/tags/awk/</link><description>Recent content in Awk on Min Soe Han</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 12 Jan 2026 16:20:19 +0630</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://minsoehan.com/tags/awk/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>AWK Basic</title><link>https://minsoehan.com/tech/awk/getting-started/</link><pubDate>Mon, 12 Jan 2026 16:20:19 +0630</pubDate><guid>https://minsoehan.com/tech/awk/getting-started/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Awk is a programming language that can handle and manipulate data. Suppose we have the following data file.&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;div class="code-header"&gt;
 &lt;div class="text"&gt;datafile.txt&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="copy-code-below"&gt;&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-copy"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight" text="datafile.txt"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#e6edf3;background-color:#0d1117;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;orange 22.5 0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;banana 19.5 12
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;apple 23.0 0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mango 25.0 30
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;papaya 22.5 25&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Print only certain field, first field for instance.&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;div class="code-header"&gt;
 &lt;div class="text"&gt;~&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="copy-code-below"&gt;&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-copy"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#e6edf3;background-color:#0d1117;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;awk &lt;span style="color:#a5d6ff"&gt;&amp;#39;{print $1}&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; datafile.txt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Print the lines (the whole line, &lt;code&gt;$0&lt;/code&gt;) with value at third field is greater than 0.&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;div class="code-header"&gt;
 &lt;div class="text"&gt;~&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="copy-code-below"&gt;&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-copy"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#e6edf3;background-color:#0d1117;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;awk &lt;span style="color:#a5d6ff"&gt;&amp;#39;$3 &amp;gt; 0 {print $0}&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; datafile.txt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do some maths &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;(value at second field is multiplied by value at third field)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; and print.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>